WHO AM I?

Hi, I am Devyani Goil , an inquisitive computer science enthusiast working at Apple in California. I completed my masters in Computer Science from University of Massachusetts, Amherst . With experience spanning distributed systems, cloud technologies, backend development and scalable system design, I thrive at the intersection of creativity and technology.

I am a highly adaptive and flexible individual actively looking for internship opportunity in Software Development where I can leverage my experience, technical expertise, and problem solving skills and build applications specific to the business needs of the company and help improve the lives of those around me. My experience with hackathons and academic projects has nurtured my ability to adapt, innovate, and communicate effectively, ensuring cohesive teamwork. With a focus on continuous improvement, I bring fresh perspectives to complex challenges, ensuring my contributions are both impactful and sustainable.
